        public void onKeyPressed(javafx.scene.input.KeyEvent event)
        Handles the user pressing a button on their keyboard. Pans the board if W, A, S or D are pressed. Increases the panning speed if shift is pressed. Toggles the simulation when Q is pressed. Steps one frame forward when E is pressed.
        Parameters:
        event - Keyboard event.

      • onKeyReleased
